metadata.name: Ghost Flood
metadata.description: "Ghost Flood" is a collaborative piece between Ghostskater and Flooding Factory, combining their artistic styles. Ghostskater will paint a limited number of physical versions of the artwork using black light and neon acrylic. The visually striking piece merges abstract, bold graphics, and digital animations with comics, cartoons, patterns, and psychedelia, reflecting the artists' desire to blend their styles. The title "Ghost Flood" reflects the merging of their respective styles.
